data.description: Located in beautiful La  Conterra, this well maintained home is ready for new owners! This Quality Buffington home has been gently lived in This lovely home is conveniently located in La Conterra! The absence of carpet, hardwood flooring, and tile in the main living areas and bathrooms is a great feature for easy maintenance. The deluxe 42" kitchen cabinets, breakfast bar, and covered patio add to the convenience and comfort of the home.  Additionally, the inclusion of a water softener and full irrigation system are practical amenities that many homeowners appreciate. The low tax rate of 1.9632 is definitely a positive aspect, contributing to the overall affordability of the property.
